I should mention that this is an expensive hotel but you really get your money’s worth in terms of quality service, property and location.	I highly recommend the hotel if you can get a room there on points (it's actually pretty hard to get room there on points) or if you can afford to pay the high price.	Overall a very enjoyable stay however dont pay much extra for the exec room as its not worth it (but I would recommend the suites).	While there are less expensive addresses and hotels in which to stay in Rome, I would definetly recommend the Grand Flora for a full, enriching experience.